{"tid":1474064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"假聯署，唔好簽，以後睇清楚聯署啲咩至簽","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:57:24.000Z","uid":278975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7740a0ff85b094d66365e4e36da4798a715ab51","tid":1474064,"uid":278975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"假聯署<br />\n同身邊嘅人講「唔好簽」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現【假】五大訴求聯署<br />\n好多人冇睇內文中伏<br />\n內文話要政府做出五大訴求，然而五大訴求係要求政府嚴正執法鎮壓運動！<br />\n<br />\n文宣組唔該幫手宣揚呢個聯署係假嘅（內文係支持政府鎮壓）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/香港受夠了-五大訴求-撥亂反正-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%A0%E4%BA%86-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%92%A5%E4%BA%82%E5%8F%8D%E6%AD%A3-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=0844a149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/香港受夠了-五大訴求-撥亂反正-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order</a><br />\n<br />\n對家仲諗住登報紙聲稱好多人支持，已經有幾萬人簽咗！<br />\n另外中共開始用三毛四方八面入侵，話示威者暴力同滿口謊言，文宣一定要大大力咁還擊！否則後果不堪設想！<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n<br />\n但係要同人講<br />\n個聯署係假嘅！<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔推唔到post，求各位巴打幫幫手！"},{"pid":"992c5c3a59b6f4e0ba6f7b34543e85412fc1fa9f","tid":1474064,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"b39df8646aeaff6cb2704db32f27610a379269de","tid":1474064,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"睇清楚內容先簽好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}